videos.headline: Smith connects with White for Boston College's first TD
videos.description: Off a reverse, former quarterback Jeff Smith finds an open Kobay White for a 34-yard touchdown to give the Eagles an early lead.

videos.headline: Trick play puts Florida State in the red zone
videos.description: James Blackman laterals to running back Cam Akers who goes deep and finds an open Nyqwan Murray for a 47-yard pass to put the Seminoles in the red zone.

videos.headline: Akers has costly fumlbes
videos.description: On second-and-goal, Cam Akers is stripped and the ball is recovered by Boston College's Will Harris.

videos.headline: Boston College pads lead with TD
videos.description: Anthony Brown finds Tommy Sweeney for an 11-yard touchdown to increase the Eagles' lead over the Seminoles.

videos.headline: Florida State turns it over again with interception
videos.description: James Blackman's pass is picked off by Ty Schwab, the second turnover of the game for the Seminoles.

videos.headline: Brown stumbles into the end zone
videos.description: Eagles' quarterback Anthony Brown scrambles to find an open receiver and runs the ball in himself for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Blackman gets banged up on hard hit
videos.description: James Blackman gets roughed up on a pass attempt that would lead to a Florida State field goal in the final seconds of the second quarter.

videos.headline: Addazio: 'We still have more stuff to throw at them'
videos.description: Boston College coach Steve Addazio breaks down how his team needs to keep the momentum rolling into the second half and the importance of the Red Bandana game.

videos.headline: Florida State suffers third turnover
videos.description: On the punt, Tarvarus McFadden fumbles and the ball is recovered by Boston College in great field position.

videos.headline: Dillon muscles his way into the end zone
videos.description: AJ Dillon pushes his way into the end zone for a two-yard touchdown to pad the Eagles' lead.

videos.headline: Wade scores first career rushing TD
videos.description: On fourth-and-goal, Darius Wade scores his first career rushing touchdown on a 1-yard run for Boston College.

videos.headline: Crowther's father shares appreciation for Boston College
videos.description: Jefferson Crowther gets emotional talking about his son and the support from the Boston College community.

videos.headline: Addazio:'We're going to continue to grow'
videos.description: Steve Addazio lays out the importance of  Boston College's 35-3 win over Florida State and how the Red Bandana game is always special for the team.
